data.description: **STILL ALLOWING SHOWINGS & ACCEPTING OFFERS** Introducing an exquisite luxury home nestled on a private 1.72-acre lot, this 4-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom masterpiece spans an impressive 5,217 square feet of living space. A  3-car garage welcomes you with a freshly sealed driveway (October 2023), leading to an impeccably landscaped garden with a zoned irrigation system.   Step inside to discover the epitome of sophistication, where pristine hardwood floors grace the main areas on the first floor. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the gourmet kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances, to the spacious living and dining areas. Large windows flood the space with natural light, offering serene garden views. Upstairs, four generously sized bedrooms provide comfort and privacy, one bedroom includes its own separate bathroom while the other two share a jack-and-jill style bathroom. The primary suite is a retreat in itself, featuring a luxurious en-suite bathroom and ample closet space, as well as its own sitting area overlooking the backyard.   The space and beauty does not stop there, the basement has been finished for you creating the ideal entertaining space on a rainy day, late evening or anytime. Featuring a wet-bar that includes a built-in mini fridge, additional space for a wine cooler or larger refrigerator, an oversized game room, a workout room with padded floors, a den which could be used for guest or an additional office, a full bathroom, and two unfinished storage areas, your guest will never want to leave.   Outside, a deck with a charming pergola invites you to unwind and entertain in style, enjoy evenings by the fire pit on the patio, wood work out of your shed, or garden for hours with the ease of maintenance as it has its own irrigation. This property features your very own fruit trees as well and additional landscape for privacy. This home is truly move in ready, even with your fur babies in mind - there is an invisible fence already installed at the property . If your own private pool is something your heart desires for your future, there is no need to worry as this lot will accommodate an in-ground pool. This meticulously designed luxury home epitomizes elegance and tranquility, offering a haven for those seeking the finest in living.
